## Features Implemented:

### Pre-Slaughter Animal Inspection (Goal-1):
- **Event 1**: Access animal inspection module (UIE)
- **Event 2**: Select animal ID from queue (UIE) 
- **Event 3**: Conduct visual & health check (OP)
- **Event 4**: Enter findings in inspection form (UIE)
- **Event 5**: Submit inspection status (OP)
- **Event 6**: Notify factory supervisor (OP)

### Hygiene Checklist Verification (Goal-2):
- **Event 1**: Login to hygiene system (UIE)
- **Event 2**: Select relevant cleaning batch (UIE)
- **Event 3**: Review auto-generated sanitation checklist (UIE)
- **Event 4**: Confirm item-by-item verification (UIE)
- **Event 5**: Upload photographic proof (UIE)
- **Event 6**: Submit report to compliance log (OP)

