This fix resolves the `IllegalAccessException` error that was preventing JavaFX from accessing the model classes' properties for the TableView columns. The PropertyValueFactory will now be able to call the getter methods (like `getBatchId()`, `getQualityStatus()`, etc.) on the model objects to populate the table cells.

